evs.metric.parameters
Interface MetricParameter

All Known Implementing Classes:
BooleanArrayParameter, BooleanParameter, BootstrapParameter, BoxPooledLeadPointsParameter, BoxUnpooledObsPointsParameter, BoxUnpooledPointsParameter, CentralSpreadBiasParameter, DecomposeParameter, DoubleArrayParameter, DoubleParameter, DoubleProcedureArrayParameter, DoubleProcedureParameter, EqualSamplesParameter, FittedAUCParameter, FittedROCParameter, ForecastTypeParameter, IntegerParameter, MCRPointsParameter, MEPPointsParameter, MinimumSampleSizeParameter, PositiveIntegerParameter, ProbabilityArrayParameter, ProbabilityIdentifierParameter, ProbabilityIntervalParameter, ProbabilityParameter, RankHistSampleParameter, ReferenceForecastParameter, ReliabilityPointsParameter, ROCPointsParameter, ROCScoreMethodParameter, ROCScorePointsParameter, SpreadBiasPointsParameter, StringArrayParameter, StringParameter, UnconditionalParameter, VectorFunctionParameter
public interface MetricParameter

An interface for the parameters required by a verification metric. Define appropriate subclasses for different parameter types, such as probability thresholds.

Version:
4.0
Author:
evs@hydrosolved.com
